        "content": "<p>zhen9910 opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12044\">PR #12044</a> from <code>zhen9910:zkong/update-ort-and-onnx-gpu</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>As discussed in <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/8547\">https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/8547</a>, the existing wasi-nn onnx backend only uses the default CPU execution provider. This PR updated the onnxruntime crate <code>ort</code> to 2.0.0-rc.10 with improved cuda support and added onnx-cuda based wasi-nn GPU execution target in <code>wasmtime-wasi-nn</code> onnx backend.</p>\n</blockquote>",
